.triangle_bg_3.white_txt.vspace
  .container
    .row.centered
      .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
        %h3.ouishare_stencil
          Guiding principles
        %hr.pink
        %br
        %br
      .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
        %h6
          %span.bluebg
            These are 14 key principles that are guiding us in the OuiShare Fest program and experience design.
        %br
        %br
        %table.criteria
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 4}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/ask.png', :alt => 'Ask'}
              %p.left
                Ask the right questions
            %td{:colspan => 7}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/enable.png', :alt => 'Enable'}
              %p.left
                Enable interaction, participation and collaboration
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 5}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/design.png', :alt => 'Design'}
              %p.right
                Design constructive confrontation: challenge ideas, expose multiple perspectives.
            %td{:colspan => 6}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/promote.png', :alt => 'Promote'}
              %p.left
                Promote extraordinary ideas and meaningful projects, not the most popular ones.
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 6}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/distill.png', :alt => 'Distill'}
              %p.left
                Distill meaning from complexity.
            %td{:colspan => 5}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/communicate.png', :alt => 'Communicate'}
              %p.right
                Communicate clearly and with purpose. 
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 4}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/stay.png', :alt => 'Stay'}
              %p.left
                Stay grounded. Be real. Donâ€™t ignore the pressing issues of our times.
            %td{:colspan => 4}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/highlight.png', :alt => 'Highlight'}
              %p.right
                Highlight new content and fresh approaches.
            %td{:colspan => 3}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/make.png', :alt => 'Make'}
              %p.left
                Make it a learning experience.
          %tr
            %td{:rowspan => 2, :colspan => 5}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/welcome.png', :alt => 'Welcome'}
              %p.left
                Welcome people as their full selves: mind, body and soul.
            %td{:colspan => 6}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/consider.png', :alt => 'Consider'}
              %p.left
                Consider all levels: individuals, teams, organisations, systems.
          %tr
            %td{:rowspan => 2, :colspan => 6}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/ensure.png', :alt => 'Ensure'}
              %p.justify
                Ensure OuiShare Fest is only a pit-stop on a continuous journey we are on together. 
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 5}
              %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/strive.png', :alt => 'Strive'}
              %p.left
                Strive for diversity of origin and gender.
            / %td
            /   %img.right{:src => '/assets/criteria/ensure.png', :alt => 'Ensure'}
            /   %p.right
            /     Ensure OuiShare Fest is only a pit-stop on a continuous journey we are on together. 
          %tr
            %td{:colspan => 11}
              %img.left{:src => '/assets/criteria/have.png', :alt => 'Have'}
              %p.left
                Have fun, smile and be open. Donâ€™t take oneself too seriously.

